BioHermes
=========

BioHermes is a downstream distribution of Hermes Agent tailored for
bioinformatics research workflows.  It adds a bio-specialized skill
library, an MCP shim that provides BioClaw-compatible `send_image` /
`send_file` tools, and an opinionated CLI config preset.

